title: 47 Minecraft Item Facts You Possibly Didn't Know
author: Skip the Tutorial
description:
47 Minecraft Item Facts You Possibly Didn't Know! Minecraft has dozens of items to choose from, so it can be easy to lose track of all the information. In that case, let's cover the top Minecraft facts about items you maybe missed. Today, Skip the Tutorial is joined by Block Facts to talk about some of the best Minecraft Item facts. If you enjoyed 47 Minecraft Block Facts You Possibly Didn’t Know and 47 Minecraft Mob Facts You Possibly Didn't Know, this is the Minecraft list video for you!

Check out @Block Facts !
